Attribution & provenance
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Emberwake is an independent, clean-room project. It was inspired by the
self-hosted startpage concept popularized by Flame
(https://github.com/pawelmalak/flame, by Paweł Malak and contributors) and its
fork Dragons-Flame. Emberwake shares NO source code, stylesheets, icon art, or
other assets with either project and is not a derivative work of them. The
inspiration is acknowledged here with thanks.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party software
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This software depends on third-party Rust crates and system libraries, each
distributed under its own license. A complete dependency inventory and license
report is produced by `cargo deny` and the generated SBOM (CycloneDX) attached
to each release. Any third-party source code vendored directly into this
repository (currently: none) will be listed here with its license.
